{"text_id":26582,"tokens":["This"," paper"," presents"," a"," comprehensive"," study"," of"," jets",","," bla","z","ars",","," and"," the"," extra","galactic"," background"," light"," (","E","BL",")"," in"," the"," context"," of"," the"," Gamma","-","ray"," Large"," Area"," Space"," Telescope"," (","G","LAST",")"," and"," the"," Ener","getic"," X","-","ray"," Imaging"," Survey"," Telescope"," (","EXIST",")"," era","."," We"," discuss"," the"," theoretical"," and"," observational"," aspects"," of"," these"," phenomena",","," focusing"," on"," their"," implications"," for"," high","-","energy"," astro","physics","."," We"," review"," the"," current"," understanding"," of"," the"," formation"," and"," propagation"," of"," jets"," from"," active"," galactic"," nuclei"," (","AG","N","),"," and"," the"," role"," of"," bla","z","ars"," as"," powerful"," sources"," of"," gamma"," rays","."," We"," also"," delve"," into"," the"," impact"," of"," the"," E","BL"," on"," the"," propagation"," of"," these"," gamma"," rays",","," considering"," both"," absorption"," and"," scattering"," processes","."," The"," potential"," of"," G","LAST"," and"," EXIST"," to"," provide"," new"," insights"," into"," these"," topics"," is"," highlighted",","," with"," a"," particular"," emphasis"," on"," the"," detection"," and"," character","ization"," of"," high","-","red","shift"," bla","z","ars"," and"," the"," measurement"," of"," the"," E","BL","."," The"," paper"," concludes"," with"," a"," discussion"," of"," the"," challenges"," and"," prospects"," for"," future"," research"," in"," this"," field","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"gpt4","label":1}